{"tid":2432400,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無公司成日搞team building?","createTime":"2021-03-04T09:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T15:20:20.000Z","uid":232400,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc903d1511c2afac95b6b89632b4fdc15961654","tid":2432400,"uid":232400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n嗌幾句濕鳩口號就想增加士氣<br />\n玩完啲game再叫你講諗法係入面學到啲咩<br />\n咩叫團隊合作 咩叫正向思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算吹水都話你講得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有野都係老細認為work 就算搞完team building第日番工啲人都係面阻阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明唔想參加都要扮到好投入要好高參與度 <br />\n成個畫面係老細眼中要好靚 好有team work<br />\n話要做到公司上下一條心咁 聽到都打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話team building 學到啲乜？真心答你唔到。<br />\n我正係學到如何面對尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實搞咁多野 實際啲不如加人工好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933f8cf337d62cecde5c14d1744ee0c26baf28c9","tid":2432400,"uid":20241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"你識啲乜<br />\nteam building唔係愛嚟俾你有冇用<br />\n而係hr用嚟表現自己存在價值嘅活動<br />\n同啲濕鳩marketing呀pr一鳩樣<br />\n懶係專業<br />\n其實啲嘢係人都識做，俾錢係fb落廣告我唔識咩？<br />\n覆ig覆fb我唔識咩？分分鐘仲係inhouse判出去做tim"},{"pid":"044630edfc7835814ccca25e58dcf92c1ab40b74","tid":2432400,"uid":290080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"只要你唔尷尬，尷尬既就係其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6d05b65dd279c355b1c6043f0554e1c2d51225","tid":2432400,"uid":199050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"保險佬"},{"pid":"a2590363841713b608885edef52173c9a025e9ac","tid":2432400,"uid":379629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11: